Even more functional-ish features: most block-based constructs are actually parse transforms on top of HoFs. For instance<p><pre><code>    for 5.times {
        // code
    }
</code></pre>
desugars to:<p><pre><code>    // |args*| { stmt* } is the Rust block syntax
    times(5, || {
        // code
        true // explicit order to continue
    })</code></pre>
